==English==
=== Proper Noun ===
'''Euphrates'''
# A 1700-kilometre-long river in Southwest [[Asia]]. It flows Southwest and Southeast from East [[Turkey]]. It forms the Western edge of classical [[Mesopotamia]]. It unites with the [[Tigris]] before flowing into the [[Persian Gulf]].

